high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn left and then right to face the toaster.
Face and look at the toaster on the counter.
Turn left and face the cabinet in the lower right hand corner and open it.
Open the cabinet in the lower right hand corner.
Place the knife in the cabinet and close it.
Turn right and take some tomato from the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave.
Open the microwave on the counter and heat it up, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn right, then right again to face the green trash-can.
Throw the tomato in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a tomato to throw away.

high_descs: turn left, go forward to sink
pick up knife from sink on the left of lettuce
turn to the left
go to counter with toaster to the left of the sink, slice tomato
turn left, go to cabinet to the right of stove
open cabinet, place knife in front left corner of cabinet, close cabinet
go to right to counter with toaster
pick up tomato slice next to toaster
turn right, go to microwave
place tomato slice in microwave, turn on microwave, remove tomato slice from microwave
turn around, go to green can to left of stove
place tomato slice in green can
anns.task_desc: place microwaved tomato slice in green can

high_descs: Turn left and go towards the sink.  At the table go left then right to get to the sink.
Go in front of the sink.
Turn left and go to the toaster.
Turn and face the toaster on the counter.
Turn right.  Open the cabinet that is to the right of the stove under the counter.
Shut the door to the cabinet.
Turn to the right.  Face the toaster that is on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato that is on the counter.
Turn to the right.  Move to the microwave.
Open the microwave.  Put the tomato slice in the microwave and shut the door.  Turn on the microwave.  Open the door when it is done and take the tomato slice out.
Turn to the right and then turn to the right again. Move towards the stove.  At the stove turn left and then right.
Put the tomato slice in the green trash can that is on the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Warm up a tomato slice to throw it away.
